      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's more than just \"theories\" though. i've been tracking it. every time i listen to certain playlists, my anxiety spikes and i feel like i can't make simple decisions. it feels intentional. do you think a company or something could actually hide these signals in the streaming data without anyone noticing? like, how would they even hide it?",
